{"title":"数据库在新建表的时候添加注释comment on column","date":"2018-07-02T20:02:00.000Z","link":"post/133","categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:17:32.010Z","content":"<p>格式：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">comment on column 表名.字段名 is &apos;注释&apos;；</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>demo<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create TABLE HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP</span><br><span class=\"line\">(</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tStoreHouseID\tvarchar(20) ,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tDeptCode\tvarchar(20),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tInStockCode\tvarchar(20),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tInStockCodeLine\tnumeric(4,0),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tDrugCode\tvarchar(20),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tUnit\tvarchar(20),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tCount\tNumeric(10,2),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tPrice\tNumeric (10,4),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tSellPrice\tNumeric (10,4),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tTotal\tNumeric (16,4),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tManufacture\tvarchar(100),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tValidity\tvarchar(10),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tFactDate\tdate,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tRemark\tvarchar(100),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tOperator\tvarchar(20),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tCZJC\tchar(1)</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.StoreHouseID  is &apos;药库编码&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.DeptCode  is &apos;药房编码&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.InStockCode  is &apos;退库单号&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.InStockCodeLine  is &apos;序号&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.DrugCode  is &apos;药品编码&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Unit  is &apos;计量单位&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Count  is &apos;数量&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Price  is &apos;进货价&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.SellPrice  is &apos;零售价&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Total  is &apos;金额&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Manufacture  is &apos;生产厂家&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Validity  is &apos;失效日期&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.FactDate  is &apos;退货日期&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Remark  is &apos;备注&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.Operator  is &apos;操作员工号&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">comment on column HPD_INSTOCK_TEMP.CZJC  is &apos;操作进程&apos;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"微信小程序获得服务器ip","link":"post/134"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序—如何获取用户输入文本框的值k.detail.value","link":"post/131"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/133/"}